OPEN MIC NIGHT: 
So this week I hit a creative slump and with the help of my IG family, I began to experiment with apps I've had forever, but hadn't touched in a while. The above shot was done with my new Olloclip wide angle lens and Dramatic Black&White app. And my new #kewiki_skyburst series is done with PhotoWizard.

So, my open mic question this week is: "Who or what inspires you to experiment on IG and what are some apps you like to use?" Let's discuss!
